大祭</strong>資訊,大部分都近東京"},{"pid":"d9ec2063b011c57d430da05cd468d9cdbdf0215c","tid":591411,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61f148792aedc33ccbe865ae60b02be0d6203015","tid":591411,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"又係你"},{"pid":"865826d337bca087db9d76560c328610b7e27d43","tid":591411,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"PS.例大祭係冇煙花的<br />\n通常睇下人表演/跳舞咁, 玩下攤位, 行下神社咁<br />\n至於其他我都唔清楚做乜<br />\n日本仔同我講日本大大小小都十鳩幾萬種祭典<br />\n佢自己都好難分得清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b028457c7a0a15b69d5787abad9a47e1f1b43a8","tid":591411,"uid":165991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46fc0d28699c8c3ede2d2244709d07b5f3be76cc","tid":591411,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebea291fce2a3c67e9b1b452e343f790b12bf5c8","tid":591411,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T01:38:32.000Z","msg":"去過九州個啲花火大會同小型祭典 <br />\n好過關東 熱鬧得黎唔算逼<br />\n最撚痴線一定係隅田川 行步路都行唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"我去過宮島個個<br />\n好辛苦<br />\n仲多人過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:41:47.000Z","msg":"祭典一定會多人<br />\n試過八月去種子島火箭祭<br />\n成個島嘅人都齊集南種子町<br />\n下午睇巡遊<br />\n夜晚放煙花<br />\n不過係好開心&hellip;"},{"pid":"f5308da60af81c5ff05dc7f65b725b431b627526","tid":591411,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9ec2063b011c57d430da05cd468d9cdbdf0215c","tid":591411,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61f148792aedc33ccbe865ae60b02be0d6203015","tid":591411,"uid":135293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"Lm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"又係你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T14:43:33.000Z","msg":